videos.headline: Brown reaches over goal line for Penn State TD
videos.description: Penn State's Journey Brown is able to keep his knees off the ground as he crosses the goal line for a 2-yard score.

videos.headline: Brown bounces his way into end zone
videos.description: Journey Brown cuts left then bounces back right into an open hole and then turns on the jets for a Penn State TD.

videos.headline: Brown runs in his 3rd touchdown of the game
videos.description: Journey Brown pulls off the hat trick and runs in his third touchdown to increase Penn State's lead to 27-6.
